ult de Meymont的兒子，於大約1180年出生在法國奧維普-德-o奧利格斯。他於1235年與Béatrix de Baffie在法國奧維-o-阿爾培斯普-德-o奧利格斯結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。他去世於1252年10月在他的家鄉享年73歲。"},"zh-hans":{"environ 1180–octobre 1252":"大约1180年–1252年10月","1180–1252":"1180年–1252年","1210–1279":"1210年–1279年","1230–1272":"1230年–1272年","1142–1222":"1142年–1222年","–1250":"–1250年","octobre 1252":"1252年10月","1235":"1235年","1279":"1279年","1222":"1222年","1210":"1210年","1230":"1230年","1142":"1142年","1252":"1252年","1250":"1250年","1272":"1272年","environ 1180":"大约1180年","1180":"1180年","Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, France":"法国奧維普-德-o奧利格斯","Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"法国奧維-o-阿爾培斯普-德-o可勒爾蒙吉福藍德","Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"法国奧維-o-阿爾培斯普-德-o奧利格斯","lifeSummary":"Agne V d'Olliergues是Robert de Clermont de Velay和Iseult de Meymont的儿子，于大约1180年出生在法国奧維普-德-o奧利格斯。他于1235年与Béatrix de Baffie在法国奧維-o-阿爾培斯普-德-o奧利格斯结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1252年10月在他的家乡享年73岁。"},"hr":{"environ 1180–octobre 1252":"oko 1180.–listopad 1252.","1180–1252":"1180–1252","1210–1279":"1210–1279","1230–1272":"1230.–1272","1142–1222":"1142–1222.","–1250":"–1250.","octobre 1252":"listopad 1252.","1235":"1235.","1279":"1279","1222":"1222.","1210":"1210","1230":"1230.","1142":"1142","1252":"1252","1250":"1250.","1272":"1272","environ 1180":"oko 1180.","1180":"1180","Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, France":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne, Francuska","Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, Francuska","Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France":"Olliergues, Puy-de-Dôme, Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, Francuska"},"cs":{"environ 1180–octobre 1252":"okolo 1180–říjen 1252","1180–1252":"1180–1252","1210–1279":"1210–1279","1230–1272":"1230–1272","1142–1222":"1142–1222","–1250":"–1250","octobre 1252":"říjen 1252","1235":"1235","1279":"1279","1222":"1222","1210":"1210","1230":"1230","1142":"1142","1252":"1252","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","environ 1180":"okolo 1180"